Katakan aku tidak di sini.

540
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:31,399
Istri Anda datang.

541
00:34:32,899 --> 00:34:34,429
Apa? Siapa yang datang?

542
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:38,030
Dia benar-benar di sini?

543
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:39,039
Ya.

544
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:43,439
Bagaimana penampilanku?

545
00:34:44,270 --> 00:34:47,140
Agak lusuh.

546
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:49,009
Lusuh?

547
00:34:54,850 --> 00:34:57,020
Pak Cha, kamu boleh pulang.

548
00:34:57,850 --> 00:34:58,859
Baik, Pak.

549
00:35:16,469 --> 00:35:17,670
Seol Ah, kamu di sini.

550
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:19,409
Ada apa kamu kemari?

551
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:21,450
Kenapa kamu belum pulang?

552
00:35:22,709 --> 00:35:25,519
Aku baru akan pulang.

553
00:35:26,319 --> 00:35:27,519
Duduklah.

554
00:35:34,890 --> 00:35:36,159
Kamu tidur di sini?

555
